	(text "Prevent signal latch up on the inputs and outputs\ngoing to the other board.  It appears when the board\nis powered down, signals can go into latchup.  For\ninstance, OTHER_HW_POWER_ST can be pulled to\nground and mess things up.  Prevent latch up from\ncausing problems using these MOSFETs."
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 241.808 154.686 0)
		(effects
